{"tid":2510551,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前民政局政治助理黎穎瑜唔返猩加坡 將任港台主持","createTime":"2021-04-30T08:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T10:32:29.000Z","uid":230530,"like":10,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"56daeb987e901544ffa1208bda946d0a9360c0b4","tid":2510551,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"今年年初請辭的前民政事務局政治助理黎穎瑜，將轉任香港電台主持。前任行政長官及政治委任官員離職後工作諮詢委員會宣布，批准黎穎瑜擔任3份工作，包括港台節目主持、為中華國術總會撰寫功夫書籍，及擔任音樂兒童基金會項目顧問。<br />\n<br />\n44歲的黎穎瑜去年12月宣誓擁護《基本法》和效忠特區，一個月後以照顧家人為由請辭。她當時在社交網站透露，因為丈夫回流新加坡，她決定跟隨照顧年幼兒子。"},{"pid":"3dd9f406eaccc9d65dd9a3f62b798cf370407550","tid":2510551,"uid":358691,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"有痛腳俾人揸住？腥家玻都唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9848eff157a6874c14eb62e6c06a32b61bb83324","tid":2510551,"uid":358691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3dd9f406eaccc9d65dd9a3f62b798cf370407550","tid":2510551,"uid":358691,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"有痛腳俾人揸住？腥家玻都唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"腥加坡*"},{"pid":"a7ce877e040a1462b8025190016073119347c5d6","tid":2510551,"uid":112747,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"逃脫失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同大波驊一樣"},{"pid":"826d69c9709e3127f717b6d10dc800541da08ca1","tid":2510551,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"繼續做狗"},{"pid":"80e1ac605066778775a20a8eb3c03cc4aff628cd","tid":2510551,"uid":54627,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"共產黨：別讓黎穎瑜跑了&gt;&gt;黎穎瑜